window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>As Saber and Caro struggle to understand their relationship, bonds are tested as secrets get revealed. With the demons and Savages closing in, the Alliance must come together to defeat their enemies, but not all will survive. Who will remain standing at the end of the battle?</p> <p>Download <i>Bound by Love, </i>the nail-biting conclusion to the Alliance series, and find out now.</p> <p>***The Alliance series is a spin-off of the Vampire Awakenings series. You do not have to listen to The Vampire Awakenings series to follow The Alliance series.***</p>"; 
